### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:10021
@user_uuid = 99faa897-1522-4dbd-ac6f-c983e55e026c
@batch_uuid = 141acd12-01f7-4221-9d96-eb180462ce99
@image_uuid = 5fe06462-c7d9-437a-99b1-d55e78282929
@node_id = node-1

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### --- IMAGES ---

### 2. Register Image (JSON)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/images
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_uuid": "{{user_uuid}}",
    "batch_uuid": "{{batch_uuid}}",
    "image_uuid": "{{image_uuid}}",
    "file_name": "test_image.jpg"
}

### 3. Get Image Info (Using PureJSON for clean URLs)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/images/{{image_uuid}}

### 4. Download Image
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/images/{{image_uuid}}/download

### 5. Update Image Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/images/{{image_uuid}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "PROCESSED"
}

### 6. Update Image Result (Worker simulation)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/images/{{image_uuid}}/result
X-Node-Id: {{node_id}}
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

<dummy_image_data_binary>

### --- BATCHES ---

### 7. Register Batch (JSON)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/batches/upload
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_uuid": "{{user_uuid}}",
    "batch_uuid": "{{batch_uuid}}"
}

### 8. List User Batches
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/batches?user_uuid={{user_uuid}}

### 9. Get Batch Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/batches/{{batch_uuid}}

### 10. Get Batch Images (Paginated with PureJSON)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/batches/{{batch_uuid}}/images?page=1&limit=10

### 11. Update Batch Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/batches/{{batch_uuid}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "COMPLETED"
}

### 12. Save Batch Transformations
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/batches/{{batch_uuid}}/transformations
Content-Type: application/json

[
    {
        "name": "grayscale",
        "params": "{}",
        "execution_order": 1
    },
    {
        "name": "resize",
        "params": "{\"width\": 800, \"height\": 600}",
        "execution_order": 2
    }
]

### --- NODES ---

### 13. Register Node
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": "{{node_id}}",
    "name": "Worker Node 1",
    "ip": "127.0.0.1",
    "port": 50051,
    "status": "IDLE"
}

### 14. List Nodes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/nodes

### 15. Get Node
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/nodes/{{node_id}}

### 16. Node Heartbeat
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/nodes/{{node_id}}/heartbeat

### 17. Update Node Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/nodes/{{node_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "BUSY"
}

### --- LOGS & METRICS ---

### 18. Create Log
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "node_id": "{{node_id}}",
    "image_uuid": "{{image_uuid}}",
    "level_name": "INFO",
    "message": "Starting image transformation",
    "log_time": "2026-04-24T07:40:00Z"
}

### 19. Get Logs by Image
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/logs/{{image_uuid}}

### 20. Create Metrics
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/metrics
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "node_id": "{{node_id}}",
    "image_uuid": "{{image_uuid}}",
    "ram_used_mb": 512.5,
    "ram_total_mb": 2048,
    "cpu_percent": 15.5,
    "workers_busy": 1,
    "workers_total": 4,
    "queue_size": 0,
    "tasks_done": 10,
    "status": "HEALTHY"
}

### 21. Get Metrics by Node
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/metrics/{{node_id}}

### 22. Get Metrics by Image (New Traceability Endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/metrics/image/{{image_uuid}}

### --- USER TELEMETRY ---

### 23. User Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{user_uuid}}/statistics

### 24. User Activity Timeline (Events history)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{user_uuid}}/activity
